---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About - Rucking Revolution" description="Our mission, philosophy, the movement, and contact information" currentPage="/about">
  <div class="bg-surface py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">ABOUT</h1>
        <p class="text-lg font-serif text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Building a stronger community through consistency, personal growth, and outdoor endurance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">OUR MISSION</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Rucking Revolution aims to establish rucking as a fitness standard, making it accessible to everyone seeking a sustainable way to build strength. We believe that weighted walking is the ultimate functional exercise—a practice that develops physical durability and mental clarity. Even more, when done with others, it can create more authentic and lasting social connections and forge a community through enduring adversity together.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        We provide structured knowledge, tools, training plans, and community resources necessary for individuals and local groups to master the fundamentals of rucking, and to foster and promote a culture in which rucking is recognised as a lifelong activity for improved health and overall well-being.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">OUR PHILOSOPHY</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="p-6 border border-border card-border">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-3">DISCIPLINE FIRST</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              Rucking rewards consistency over intensity. We emphasize progressive overload, proper form, and sustainable training habits that build resilience over time.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border border-border card-border">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-3">LEADERSHIP IN MOTION</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              Every ruck is an opportunity to lead and be led. Our platform teaches leadership principles through crew dynamics, after-action reviews, and field exercises.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border border-border card-border">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-3">COMMUNITY SUSTAINS</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              Individual ruckers are strong. Rucking crews are unstoppable. We build tools and resources that help crews form, grow, and sustain their practice together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">THE MOVEMENT</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Rucking Revolution is more than a website—it's a growing network of individuals, crews, and communities who share a commitment to carrying the load together. From weekend warriors to professional ruckers, our platform serves everyone who answers the call of the weighted march.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="p-6 border border-border card-border">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-3">FOR INDIVIDUALS</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>Training programs and workout generators</li>
              <li>Performance kit guides and recommendations</li>
              <li>Route planning and event discovery</li>
              <li>Leadership development resources</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border border-border card-border">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-3">FOR CREWS</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>Crew formation and culture building</li>
              <li>After-action review systems</li>
              <li>Team training programming</li>
              <li>Event coordination tools</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">WHAT WE OFFER</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a href="/learn" class="block p-6 border border-border card-border hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-2">KNOWLEDGE BASE</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              In-depth articles, guides, and digital resources covering rucking theory, training methodology, and leadership principles.
            </p>
          </a>
          <a href="/train" class="block p-6 border border-border card-border hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-2">TRAINING PROGRAMS</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              Structured workout generators, performance kit guides, and progressive training programs for all skill levels.
            </p>
          </a>
          <a href="/lead" class="block p-6 border border-border card-border hover:border-primary transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-secondary mb-2">LEADERSHIP & CREWS</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
              Resources for building and leading rucking crews, including crew tactics, after-action reviews, and club development.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-secondary mb-4 bg-[#8a1e1e] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded">JOIN THE REVOLUTION</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Whether you're just starting out rucking or have led a crew for a long time, there's a place for you in the Rucking Revolution.<br>No Experience? Learn today to lead tomorrow.<br>Got Experience? Share and teach others.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/learn/articles" class="btn btn-primary">
            START LEARNING
          </a>
          <a href="/train" class="btn btn-secondary">
            BEGIN TRAINING
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-utility btn-get-in-touch">
            GET IN TOUCH
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
